<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
    <title>Explore Our Tax Services</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset & Base */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1554224155-6726b3ff858f') no-repeat center center/cover;
            min-height: 100vh;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }

        /* Dark overlay for readability */
        body::before {
            content: "";
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
            z-index: 0;
        }

        /* Fixed Navigation bar */
        nav {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
            padding: 15px 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 40px;
            z-index: 1000;
            backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
        }

        nav a {
            color: #f8f8f8;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            color: #ffdd57;
        }

        .container {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            max-width: 900px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin: 120px auto 50px;
            /* push content below fixed navbar */
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #f8f8f8;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: #eaeaea;
        }

        .services {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 20px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
            transition: 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }

        .card h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #ffdd57;
        }

        .card p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #f5f5f5;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            background: #ffdd57;
            color: #333;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background: #ffc107;
        }

        footer {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
            color: #f8f8f8;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 10px;
            margin-top: 40px;
            border-top: 1px solid #444;
        }

        nav {
            a {
                display: inline-block;
                padding: 10px 15px;
                border-radius: 5px;
                transition: background 0.3s;
                background: darken(#0a4b9b, 5%);
                color: #fff;
                justify-content: right;
            }

            a:hover {
                background: #0a4b9b;
            }
        }

        .social-media {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            color: #ffdd57;
            background-color: #ffdd57;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <!-- Fixed Navigation -->
    <nav>
        <a href="/home">Home</a>
        <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link" href="about-us">About Us</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link" href="contact-us">Contact Us</a>
        </li>
    </nav>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>Explore Our Tax Preparation Services</h1>
        <p>We are committed to maximizing your refund while ensuring full compliance with IRS regulations. Explore our
            wide range of professional tax preparation services tailored to meet your needs.</p>

        <div class="services">
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Personal Tax Returns</h3>
                <p>Get your individual taxes done with accuracy and care, ensuring the best possible outcome for your
                    refund.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <h3>Business Tax Filing</h3>
                <p>We help small businesses and self-employed professionals file taxes smoothly and stay compliant.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <h3>Tax Planning</h3>
                <p>Strategize your finances with our year-round tax planning services to minimize liabilities.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <h3>IRS Audit Assistance</h3>
                <p>Our experts stand by your side in case of audits, providing full representation and support.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <a href="/home" class="btn">Back to Home</a>
    </div>
</body>
<footer>
    <p>&copy; 2025 Tax-Prep Expert. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>Contact us at: <a href="mailto:info@taxprep.com" style="color: #ffdd57;">info@taxprep.com</a></p>
</footer>

</html>